{"tid":2016050,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"柒！黃秋生或入籍台灣　黃安批「給黃家丟臉」　秋生：我根本不姓黃","createTime":"2020-05-14T06:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T10:45:55.000Z","uid":213877,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"959dde96d27c89ad8184ecc10e0b3a3b075abdf9","tid":2016050,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"近日傳出影帝黃秋生將會入籍台灣，網民熱烈追問，黃秋生回應「準備中」，並指目前入境台灣是為了拍劇，台灣移民署日前（11日）指尚未收到其入籍申請。長期活躍於內地的台灣藝人黃安在微博上炮轟黃秋生，指他丟了所有姓黃的人的面子。不過批評傳到黃秋生耳中後，他冷冷回應「我根本不姓黃」，網民紛紛表示茅塞頓開，直言秋生的facebook帳戶就是「Anthony Perry」，全名叫「Anthony William Perry」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200514/337582699558604800.jpeg/69XRueiocggX06nu6DXCWwyXDhJec0qDAcwbTgHMG04?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200514%2F337582699558604800.jpeg%2F69XRueiocggX06nu6DXCWwyXDhJec0qDAcwbTgHMG04%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=864ae886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1308867/org/6b290e60b6a3d17ad699615f4f414aec.jpg/5yp01iBgA7iEVKaIKd5jzdQK24zZG8xlUncX0FJ3F9A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1308867%2Forg%2F6b290e60b6a3d17ad699615f4f414aec.jpg%2F5yp01iBgA7iEVKaIKd5jzdQK24zZG8xlUncX0FJ3F9A&h=766a8750&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eec58fdaa24c74776690180a29208d264479cbf","tid":2016050,"uid":215582,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"媽，好撚柒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a91be8dee140a56b699eaf6c57b86dee4a2b81","tid":2016050,"uid":213877,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2eec58fdaa24c74776690180a29208d264479cbf","tid":2016050,"uid":215582,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:17:11.000Z"